# Clean Architecture Implementation for LeetCode User Verification

I'll implement a clean architecture approach for your LeetCode user verification functionality. This will include:

1. Data layer (Repository, Data Source, API Service)
2. Domain layer (Use Cases, Models)
3. Presentation layer (ViewModel)

Let me structure this properly:

## 1. Data Layer

```kotlin:app/src/main/java/com/devrachit/ken/data/remote/api/LeetCodeGraphqlApi.kt
